Thanks!Nice to have added sources and good not to make these normal informational “references” as that section will be removed.- Bernie (from iPad)On Jul 9, 2023, at 6:02 PM, Tomek Mrugalski ***@***.***> wrote:﻿
@bevolz, I think I addressed all your comments from 2 days ago. Thanks for reviewing!

